{"tid":2337760,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"呢位27歲男子除檢疫手環偷出街  只係80小時社會服務令？","createTime":"2020-12-23T13:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T05:28:58.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7adc513a9010397f897e969d5ad58721c8eaaff","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/23/P2020122300653.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F23%2FP2020122300653.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=585af42a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/23/P2020122300653.htm</a><br />\n 一名27歲男子因違反《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》（第599C章）（《規例》），今日（十二月二十三日）<span class=\"red\">於沙田裁判法院被判處80小時社會服務令。</span><br />\n   <br />\n  該名男子早前獲發強制檢疫令，訂明他必須在家中接受強制檢疫十四日。在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下<span class=\"red\">脫下手環，並於五月二十九日離開其檢疫地點。</span>他被控違反《規例》第8（1）、8（4）及8（5）條，今日於沙田裁判法院被判處80小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n是你嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<blockquote>沙田裁判法院  日期： 2020年12月23日 (星期三)  <br />\n裁判官 Magistrate : 溫紹明署理主任裁判官<br />\n STS 500291/2020 湯進朗 TONG, CHUN LONG 違反檢疫期間的限制 判刑 Sentence   <br />\nSTS 500292/2020 湯進朗 TONG, CHUN LONG 違反檢疫令所指明的檢疫條款 判刑 Sentence</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f67ba47be0161c80861bd6b0131acd63fa0c0f9b","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zdyj8PR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdyj8PR.gif&h=12f79686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/10/P2020121000707.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F10%2FP2020121000707.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=32dcbb14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/10/P2020121000707.htm</a><br />\n36歲男子 罰款10,000元<br />\n<br />\n該名男子為跨境貨車司機，他早前於內地遺失駕駛執照，因此須回港補領。回港時，他獲發強制檢疫令，訂明他必須在家中接受強制檢疫十四日。其後此男子的內地同事尋回駕駛執照並送回香港。<span class=\"red\">在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在未取得獲授權人員的許可下，於五月十六日離開其檢疫地點並計劃駕駛其貨車返回內地</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，他在落馬洲出入境管制站被入境事務處職員截獲。"},{"pid":"f7cb306c0945c4217ae63a3856c640ba1fd34a83","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/22/P2020122200604.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F22%2FP2020122200604.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=d3e97b73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/22/P2020122200604.htm</a><br />\n47歲男子 監禁14日<br />\n該名男子於六月二日入境時獲發強制檢疫令，訂明他必須在家中接受強制檢疫十四日。他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">於同日到入境事務處辦事處處理身份證事宜。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1454554670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1454554670.jpg&h=fdecb9f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2540b434c727c49f0933b6ff886681d0c8ce10be","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:47:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/18/P2020121800617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F18%2FP2020121800617.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=b5df1a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/18/P2020121800617.htm</a><br />\n49歲女子 監禁十四日<br />\n該名女子早前獲發強制檢疫令，訂明她必須在酒店接受強制檢疫十四日。在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，她在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，於六月二十三日離開其檢疫地點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/16/P2020121600603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F16%2FP2020121600603.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=d0d3bee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/16/P2020121600603.htm</a><br />\n58歲男子 監禁16日<br />\n   <br />\n在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，<span class=\"red\">曾三次離開其檢疫地點，並於二月二十九日在港珠澳大橋管制站被入境事務處職員截獲。</span>他被控三項違反《規例》第8（1）及8（5）條，今日於西九龍裁判法院就三項罪行各被判處即時監禁16日，同期執行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/08/P2020120800682.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F08%2FP2020120800682.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=5bd5f0f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/08/P2020120800682.htm</a><br />\n42歲男子 監禁七日，緩刑十二個月<br />\n在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，於四月二十七日離開其檢疫地點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/01/P2020120100740.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F01%2FP2020120100740.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=0483e476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/01/P2020120100740.htm</a><br />\n76歲男子 即時監禁七日 <br />\n他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，於七月十日離開其檢疫地點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/26/P2020112600675.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F26%2FP2020112600675.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=279d395d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/26/P2020112600675.htm</a><br />\n26歲女子 罰款10,000元<br />\n在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，她在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，<span class=\"red\">於五月七日的突擊檢查中，被發現脫下手環。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"red\">61歲男子 罰款10,000元</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，於三月三十日離開其檢疫地點。<br />\n <br />\n80歲男子 罰款12,000元<br />\n46歲男子 監禁七日<br />\n在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他們在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，分別於三月二十七日及七月三日離開其檢疫地點。"},{"pid":"47d26638fbcffc0b583565230c504891ecae42cd","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:50:30.000Z","msg":"最重都係第一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91176687_2954211927951208_1696324550762954752_n.png?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=iZBlkqBalg4AX93w4gf&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=3e9d106aac8e2fcf4f7d845fb8bed4b0&amp;oe=600875B9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F91176687_2954211927951208_1696324550762954752_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DiZBlkqBalg4AX93w4gf%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D3e9d106aac8e2fcf4f7d845fb8bed4b0%26oe%3D600875B9&h=01ef7f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至今共有89人因違反檢疫令被法庭定罪，被判監禁最多3個月或罰款1.5萬港元。"},{"pid":"f3b5705dd69cdc77eff12a4e45fd613e7c7077b8","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/17/P2020111700651.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F17%2FP2020111700651.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=3495b613\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/17/P2020111700651.htm</a>76歲男子 即時監禁十四日<br />\n在入境後沒有到其檢疫地點，並在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，<span class=\"red\">於同日企圖離境並在深圳灣管制站被入境事務處職員截獲。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/12/P2020111200702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F12%2FP2020111200702.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=02dc13db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/12/P2020111200702.htm</a><br />\n67歲男子 監禁六日，緩刑十二個月。<br />\n 在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，離開其檢疫地點，並於九月二十三日在深圳灣出入境管制站被入境事務處職員截獲。"},{"pid":"d9ccbb8bb5ecfcf1921a3f51a408c89927d1a235","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"三萬蚊，冇咗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/11/P2020111100747.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F11%2FP2020111100747.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=2a8e7ad4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/11/P2020111100747.htm</a><br />\n33歲男子。該名男子早前獲發強制檢疫令，訂明他必須在家中接受強制檢疫14日。在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，於三月二十三日及二十四日離開其檢疫地點。他被控兩項違反《外國地區到港人士強制檢疫規例》（第599E章）第8（1）及8（5）條，今日於東區裁判法院就兩項罪行<span class=\"red\">各被判處罰款15,000元。</span>"},{"pid":"153079041c9345420d5d91230b22ba4431ec3f43","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202009/30/P2020093000830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202009%2F30%2FP2020093000830.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=70674998\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202009/30/P2020093000830.htm</a>55歲男子，他早前獲發強制檢疫令，訂明他必須在家中接受強制檢疫十四日。其後警方接報，於五月六日在油麻地截獲該名男子。經調查後，發現該名男子在檢疫令尚未屆滿前曾獲批准外出接受治療，<span class=\"red\">但於出院後並沒有立刻返回檢疫地點</span>，並在公眾地方逗留。他被控違反《規例》第8（4）及8（5）條，今日於粉嶺裁判法院被判處即時<span class=\"red\">監禁14日。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/30/P2020103000750.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202010%2F30%2FP2020103000750.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=14a2f669\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/30/P2020103000750.htm</a><br />\n54歲女子 即時監禁八星期 <br />\n  該名女子早前獲發強制檢疫令，訂明她必須在酒店接受強制檢疫十四日。在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，她在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，於八月一日離開其檢疫地點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/20/P2020112000725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F20%2FP2020112000725.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=e2b2f485\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/20/P2020112000725.htm</a><br />\n49歲男子 即時監禁三個星期<br />\n  該名男子早前獲發強制檢疫令，訂明他必須在家中接受強制檢疫十四日。在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，於九月三十日離開其檢疫地點。"},{"pid":"beda84bf20dd1ae4e424e0bb85fcb0d0bca2dfb3","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"係屋企除手環都判監六日，人地出埋街就社會服務令<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/24/P2020112400758.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F24%2FP2020112400758.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=47cc0fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/24/P2020112400758.htm</a><br />\n23歲男子因違反《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》（第599C章）（《規例》），今日（十一月二十四日）於觀塘裁判法院被判處即時監禁六日。<br />\n   <br />\n  該名男子早前獲發強制檢疫令，訂明他必須在家中接受強制檢疫十四日。在檢疫令尚未屆滿前，他在無合理辯解及未取得獲授權人員許可下，<span class=\"red\">於五月二十日的突擊檢查中，被發現脫下手環。</span>他被控違反《規例》第8（4）及8（5）條，今日於觀塘裁判法院被判處即時監禁六日。"},{"pid":"73001e01f350f9bfbed334e3ce875b0086312364","tid":2337760,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep